<span class='tline' id='l46' data-llen='1015:1038'>　　扵其後設引禮及諸執事人位又扵其後執事者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l47' data-llen='1038:1061'>　　扵饌所實祭品扵楪内解牲體寘扵二俎寘酒扵</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l48' data-llen='1061:1084'>　　尊教讀書祝文扵紙祭品既備執事者各捧設扵</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l49' data-llen='1084:1107'>　　神位前燃香明燭自會首以下各服常服盥手入</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l50' data-llen='1107:1130'>　　就拜位立定執事者執壺扵尊中取酒立扵五土</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l51' data-llen='1130:1152'>　　神位之左引禮者唱鞠躬拜興拜興平身會首</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l52' data-llen='1152:1178'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0090', 'WYG', '005-3b' );" name="005-3b" class="pb">[005-3b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l53' data-llen='1178:1201'>　　以下皆鞠躬拜興拜興平身執事者取毛血瘞扵</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l54' data-llen='1201:1224'>　　坎中引禮者引會首詣五土神位前唱跪會首詣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l55' data-llen='1224:1254'>　　五土神位前跪舉<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR0678' title='KR0678' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0678.png'/>執壺者斟酒引禮者唱三祭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l56' data-llen='1254:1277'>　　酒會首三次傾酒少許扵地訖引禮者唱俯伏興</span><br/>
