<span class='tline' id='l58' data-llen='1300:1330'>　　五穀神位前唱跪會首詣五穀神位前跪舉<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR0678' title='KR0678' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0678.png'/>執</span><br/>
