<span class='tline' id='l74' data-llen='1682:1688'>　　尚饗</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l75' data-llen='1688:1695'>　報用仲秋</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l76' data-llen='1695:1709'>　　祭期用黄厯八月内社日</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l77' data-llen='1709:1718'>　　儀注同祈禮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l78' data-llen='1718:1741'>　　祭文同前惟改仲春東作方興作仲秋嵗事有成</span><br/>
